Enter numerator   : 10
Enter denominator : 0
Caught ArithmeticException: Denominator cannot be zero!
[finally] Block 1 executed — division operation finished.

=== Demonstration 2: throws with checked exception ===
Caught IOException: Filename is invalid or empty.
[finally] Block 2 executed — file operation finished.

