**(b)** Write a Java program that reads two integers from the user, performs division, and demonstrates `try-catch-finally` along with a method that uses `throws` to propagate an `ArithmeticException`. Show output for both `denominator = 0` and `denominator = 5` cases. **(7 marks)**

