**(a)** What is an `ActionListener`? Explain how event delegation model works in Swing with a suitable diagram. **(7 marks)**

**(b)** Modify the SimpleCalculator program to additionally support the **modulo (%)** operation, and ensure that the calculator handles both the **integer division by zero** and the **floating-point division by zero** cases correctly. Show sample input-output. **(7 marks)**

